{"tid":1454336,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"康怡廣場：有暴徒","createTime":"2019-08-12T07:02:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T10:14:07.000Z","uid":298759,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"821ca288106350a3c15381b82335e0559ab8a59b","tid":1454336,"uid":298759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T07:02:49.000Z","msg":"（轉 樂活鰂魚涌）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/266832133494362/posts/1323117741199124?s=545508086&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F266832133494362%2Fposts%2F1323117741199124%3Fs%3D545508086%26sfns%3Dmo&d=dhMoNY2Sjv1OWPDolMMhQ5dwtLMCc893KahbJtTxKsc%3D&h=7e9f287f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/266832133494362/posts/1323117741199124?s=545508086&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n大家好，我是康山花園業主。<br />\n<br />\n昨日（2019年8月11日）晚上，大量防暴警經康怡廣場進入港鐵太古站C出入口拘捕示威者，本人昨晚11時致電康怡廣場管理處（25695016）查詢為管理處會容許警方在私人地方執法，以及警方有沒有出示搜查或拘捕令。結果康怡廣場管理處職員會答我現場有暴徒，情況危險，所以警方到場處理。管理處職員沒有回答我警方有沒有出示搜查或拘捕令，同時以我從職員之解釋所得悉，相信當時管理處由於安全問題沒有派職員到場了解情況。<br />\n<br />\n今日中午時間，我再致電恆隆地產（28790111）詢問恆隆有否事前康怡廣場管理處職員商討警方到場執法之安排，暫時仍等候恆隆地產回覆。<br />\n<br />\n本人要求康怡廣場管理處：<br />\n１）解釋2019年8月11日晚上有否派職員到康怡廣場近港鐵太古站C出入口監察現場安全<br />\n２）為何容許警方在私人地方執法，以及警方有沒有出示搜查或拘捕令<br />\n３）康怡廣場管理處職員解釋憑什麼稱示威為暴徒<br />\n<br />\n本人在此呼籲各位街坊一起向恆隆地產及康怡廣場管理處了解情況及反映大家之想法，香港是我們的家，康怡康山是我們的社區。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/cEYp55prr7Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FcEYp55prr7Q&d=dhMoNY2Sjv1OWPDolMMhQ5dwtLMCc893KahbJtTxKsc%3D&h=91c8ffd2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/cEYp55prr7Q</a>"},{"pid":"c2f0d866f896ca40f723933ac78f86140a60caec","tid":1454336,"uid":303515,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T07:06:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1Fo6ODy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1Fo6ODy.jpg&h=bbc6a9d7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"85aaf2604f078084a29f2dd064374c3c37de3e91","tid":1454336,"uid":298759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T07:09:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee20657bd06ddb4962f038e8da2f7e13e16f238a","tid":1454336,"uid":298759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T07:30:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ed488763e55442d795adefc612e5f0594cd3ce3","tid":1454336,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T10:14:07.000Z","msg":"push"}]}